                            </h3>
                        </li>
                                            <li class="mv075 flex">
                            <h3 class="h5t mt0 mb025 medium">
                                <a class="theme__accent theme__text-hover" href="https://www.quantamagazine.org/the-fastest-way-yet-to-color-graphs-20250512/">
                                    <span class="' . $span_class . '">The Fastest Way Yet to Color Graphs</span>
                                </a>
                            </h3>
                        </li>
                                    </ol>
            </aside>
        </div>
        
<p>[<em>Music plays</em>]</p>
